   with one or more keywords.  Tagged items can then be located based upon tags
   and/or the individuals that tagged them.  The system also permits users to
   rate the quality of items, mark items as shared or private, and indicate
   which items are favorites.</p>
   <p class='continued'>Storing your bookmarks in connexions provided a number
